column1: ## Adult female modern specimen from Israel (id #1047), curated in
## Archaeozoology Laboratory at the University of Haifa
## Harding S, Marom N (2021). “Measurements compiled for the Zooarchaeology of
## Southern Phoenicia (ZSP) Project, from the reference collection in the Leon
## Recanati Institute for Maritime Studies (RIMS, Department of Maritime
## Civilizations, University of Haifa, Israel).” Personal communication,
## included permission to publish them as part of the package zoolog.
